{"tid":2407662,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再討論托哥條柒頭","createTime":"2021-02-14T08:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T11:18:57.000Z","uid":239081,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f37f5f95cbf38377c61d594f166ec9aefa45ad5","tid":2407662,"uid":239081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"對YouTuber 托哥 Torres 好失望<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2407206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2407206</a><br />\n<br />\n1.托哥係紅底垃圾<br />\n2.同佢條女係好無禮貌<br />\n以上兩點係事實<br />\n唔需要討論<br />\n<br />\n我覺得重點問題有幾個<br />\n<br />\n1.約定俗成嘅讀音係咪大過字典上面嘅讀音？<br />\n<br />\n例如話「時間」一詞：<br />\n普遍人會讀 時gaan3（諫）<br />\n但字典上要人讀 時gaan1（艱）<br />\n<br />\n間 - 粵語審音配詞字庫<br />\n<a href=\"https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%B6%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2Fsearch.php%3Fq%3D%25B6%25A1&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=d606a240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%B6%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n我覺得語言經過長時間演變 唔多唔少都會同原本有分別<br />\n所以我比較接受大眾讀法而非字典讀法<br />\n<br />\n2.約定俗成嘅讀音寫法應該上字典？<br />\n<br />\n如果接受大眾讀法應該取代字典讀法係咪應該收錄已改變嘅讀音 <br />\n由細到大我都覺得香港缺少一本具公信力嘅字典<br />\n好多字我都唔係好肯定點寫點讀<br />\n<br />\n嘅 既<br />\n俾 比 畀<br />\n咗 左<br />\n宜家 依家<br />\n咁 噉<br />\n緊 梗<br />\n<br />\n香港無官方寫法<br />\n我覺得應該自己投票決定<br />\n<br />\n3.真係錯嘅讀音寫法應唔應該改？<br />\n<br />\n極易讀錯嘅廣東話！你讀啱幾多個？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/f0QgMUzc3sU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ff0QgMUzc3sU&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=329b8429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/f0QgMUzc3sU</a><br />\n<br />\n當大部分人都唔識該字嘅讀音<br />\n會唔會變成約定俗成？<br />\n我自己覺得呢啲係真係要學好而唔似「時間」咁絕對多人<br />\n起碼我唔會讀錯<br />\n<br />\n玩 挽<br />\n係 系<br />\n唔 吾<br />\n<br />\n錯定約定俗成條線唔清晰<br />\n我憑感覺覺得上面三款係有正確答案<br />\n<br />\n今次講住中文先 下次再講英文<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"00b9d481352422687837292be25c14cff8167628","tid":2407662,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:08:40.000Z","msg":"who?"},{"pid":"a007213e3489ce9430afd9509d79a22a7c8ceb3e","tid":2407662,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"高大靚仔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56841f8b80ffb55826e3130317831649f30e04e","tid":2407662,"uid":239081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a007213e3489ce9430afd9509d79a22a7c8ceb3e","tid":2407662,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"高大靚仔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbfeb62b19b291014825c5e77cb206302439a69","tid":2407662,"uid":239081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00b9d481352422687837292be25c14cff8167628","tid":2407662,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:08:40.000Z","msg":"who?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:07:17.000Z","msg":"無料扮四條嘅YouTuber"},{"pid":"2679c0e94ac6e160b7377612627257c2007fd43d","tid":2407662,"uid":189417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"鬥黃就狂討論<br />\n呢d就唔討論<br />\n佢咪越做越起囉"},{"pid":"a1db2148bf188da87ea773af560e69b9cb7cf356","tid":2407662,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"托哥勁黃 手足黎 拉"},{"pid":"411e352b4439b5e774d4b68bb80ce31bc239aeec","tid":2407662,"uid":239081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2679c0e94ac6e160b7377612627257c2007fd43d","tid":2407662,"uid":189417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"鬥黃就狂討論<br />\n呢d就唔討論<br />\n佢咪越做越起囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:54:15.000Z","msg":"討論下正統香港文化好過啦"},{"pid":"91068ab4b1e3ef7a7441546158f9ab1781f8a4a1","tid":2407662,"uid":346977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:05:36.000Z","msg":"條柒頭最近有條片係講英文口音<br />\n同條女係中環challenge人哋啲英文讀得啱同唔啱<br />\nNative speakers 都畀佢challenge<br />\n條柒頭應該唔知淨係England都有幾十種accents / dialects"},{"pid":"ebfe93d59cfe7b8ee8f954cbf40bd877b3b4d93d","tid":2407662,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91068ab4b1e3ef7a7441546158f9ab1781f8a4a1","tid":2407662,"uid":346977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:05:36.000Z","msg":"條柒頭最近有條片係講英文口音<br />\n同條女係中環challenge人哋啲英文讀得啱同唔啱<br />\nNative speakers 都畀佢challenge<br />\n條柒頭應該唔知淨係England都有幾十種accents / dialects"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:18:57.000Z","msg":"真 係英國生活過就知英文讀音同一個字可以有幾種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有d 人skip t 音 有d 地方/字有唔正統音native speaker 都搞唔清亦都無人care 係香港笑人地讀錯既人真係井底之蛙"}]}